<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>و <span style="color:#950000">" الَيد "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الرِّجْل "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" العَيْن "</span> كلهَا مُؤَنّثَة.<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ الشَّاعِر:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#008000">(اليَدُّ سابِحةٌ والرِّجْلُ ضارِحَةٌ ... والعَيْنُ قادِحَةٌ والمَتْنُ مَلْحُوبُ)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" المَتْن "</span> أَيْضا مؤنث.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأنْشد:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#008000">(وَمْتنانِ خَظاتانِ ... كزُحْلُوف مِنَ الهَضْبِ)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" اليَمين "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الشَّمال "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الفَخِذ "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الوَرِك "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الكَرِش "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" العَجُز "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الضِّلَع "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" البَاع "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" العَضُد "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الكَتِف "</span> و <span style="color:#950000">" الكُراع "</span> كلهَا مُؤَنّثَة.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" العَاتِق "</span> تذكَّر وتؤنث.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>